===Other vocabulary===
A small number of vocabulary items are characteristically Ottawa.<ref>Rhodes, Richard, 1976a, pp. 150-151</ref> Although these items are robustly attested in Ottawa, they have also been reported in some other communities.<ref>Valentine, J. Randolph, 1994, pp. 430<U+2013>434; other items listed, p. 431</ref>

